title: LEGAL CLERK I/II I:$14.00-$17.09/hr. II: $15.47-$18.89/hr.
text:
LEGAL CLERK I/II I:$14.00-$17.09/hr. II: $15.47-$18.89/hr. ad date: 10/02/2015 
I:$14.00-$17.09/hr. II: $15.47-$18.89/hr. Tuolumne County Probation is seeking qualified candidates to perform legal secretarial and clerical support work for professional staff. Requires HS Dipoloma or GED equivalent with supplemental coursework in legal terminology and document format and one year of legal clerical exp. Apply online at www.tuolumnecounty.ca.gov Closes: 10/7/2015
